      "content": "i dont have ketone strips with me right now and i dont want to drive to the pharmacy if i dont have to. i'm just really stressed about the 240 reading. if i just take like 2 units of rapid acting insulin now, it should stabilize me and stop it from going even higher, right? it feels safer to just treat the number i see on the screen.",
